```plantuml
@startuml
abstract class DaoSupport {
  + void save(Object e)
  + void delete(Integer id)
}

interface PersonService {
  + void delete(Integer id)
}

class PersonServiceBean {
  + void delete(Integer id)
}

DaoSupport <|-- PersonServiceBean
PersonService <|.. PersonServiceBean

note "泛化即继承关系" as N1
DaoSupport .. N1
N1 .. PersonServiceBean

note "实现关系" as N2
PersonService .. N2
N2 .. PersonServiceBean

@enduml
```